Oh, you mean that time?
I remember. What about it?

rows.label: bf11490100_0030
rows.name:
He was supposed to talk about Metsu, but it sounded
like he could have been talking about Marveni, too.

rows.label: bf11490100_0050
rows.name: What if Metsu's actions are really Marveni'sâ€”

rows.label: bf11490100_0060
rows.name: No... what if it's the wish of all of you humans?

rows.label: bf11490100_0085
rows.name: Let's say we beat Metsu. What then?

rows.label: bf11490100_0100
rows.name: Like I told Hugo, I'll go home and work the land.

rows.label: bf11490100_0105
rows.name: I didn't get to harvest the Folta this year.

rows.label: bf11490100_0110
rows.name: That might work for you, but...

rows.label: bf11490100_0130
rows.name: I wonder if that'll be enough for everyone else...
